{"metadata":{"navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"keepScreenOn"}],"role":"symbol","modules":[{"name":"ScanbotSDK"}],"title":"keepScreenOn","fragments":[{"text":"var","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"keepScreenOn","kind":"identifier"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"text":"Bool","preciseIdentifier":"s:Sb","kind":"typeIdentifier"}],"externalID":"c:@M@ScanbotSDK@objc(cs)SBSDKBaseScannerEnergyConfiguration(py)keepScreenOn","symbolKind":"property","roleHeading":"Instance Property"},"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/scanbotsdk\/sbsdkbasescannerenergyconfiguration\/keepscreenon"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}]},{"paths":["\/documentation\/scanbotsdk\/sbsdkbasescannerenergyconfiguration\/keepscreenon"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}]}],"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/net.doo.ScanbotSDK\/documentation\/ScanbotSDK\/SBSDKBaseScannerEnergyConfiguration\/keepScreenOn","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"sections":[],"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"If enabled the idle timer of the device will be disabled while the scanner is active, preventing the device from going to sleep (dim and lock screen)."}],"schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"major":0,"patch":0},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/net.doo.ScanbotSDK\/documentation\/ScanbotSDK","doc:\/\/net.doo.ScanbotSDK\/documentation\/ScanbotSDK\/SBSDKBaseScannerEnergyConfiguration"]]},"kind":"symbol","primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"languages":["swift"],"platforms":["iOS"],"tokens":[{"text":"@objc","kind":"attribute"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"dynamic","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"var","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"keepScreenOn","kind":"identifier"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"text":"Bool","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:Sb"},{"text":" { ","kind":"text"},{"text":"get","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"set","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" }","kind":"text"}]}]}],"references":{"doc://net.doo.ScanbotSDK/documentation/ScanbotSDK/SBSDKBaseScannerEnergyConfiguration":{"url":"\/documentation\/scanbotsdk\/sbsdkbasescannerenergyconfiguration","kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The energy management configuration object for a ‘SBSDKBaseScannerViewController’ and its subclasses."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"‘SBSDKBaseScannerViewController’ and subclasses sport a customizable energy management system."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Since scanners running on a live video feed can put a lot of load onto the CPU and\/or GPU"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"of the device, causing the battery to drain quickly and running the device hot, you can customize the energy"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"consumption using this class by configuring the rate of detections\/recognitions per second in performance mode as"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"well as in energy saving mode."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"In performance mode the scanners will be fed with a higher, configurable rate of"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"video frames per second."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"After a certain, configurable period of inactivity the energy save mode will be engaged and the rate"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"of scans will be reduced to a lower (configurable) rate."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"You can also configure the time of inactivity before the automatic mode switches from performance to energy save mode."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Inactivity here means that both of the following conditions are met:"}],"role":"symbol","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"SBSDKBaseScannerEnergyConfiguration","kind":"identifier"}],"fragments":[{"text":"class","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"SBSDKBaseScannerEnergyConfiguration","kind":"identifier"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/net.doo.ScanbotSDK\/documentation\/ScanbotSDK\/SBSDKBaseScannerEnergyConfiguration","type":"topic","title":"SBSDKBaseScannerEnergyConfiguration"},"doc://net.doo.ScanbotSDK/documentation/ScanbotSDK/SBSDKBaseScannerEnergyConfiguration/keepScreenOn":{"type":"topic","identifier":"doc:\/\/net.doo.ScanbotSDK\/documentation\/ScanbotSDK\/SBSDKBaseScannerEnergyConfiguration\/keepScreenOn","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"keepScreenOn","kind":"identifier"}],"role":"symbol","abstract":[{"text":"If enabled the idle timer of the device will be disabled while the scanner is active, preventing the device from going to sleep (dim and lock screen).","type":"text"}],"fragments":[{"text":"var","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"keepScreenOn","kind":"identifier"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"text":"Bool","preciseIdentifier":"s:Sb","kind":"typeIdentifier"}],"url":"\/documentation\/scanbotsdk\/sbsdkbasescannerenergyconfiguration\/keepscreenon","kind":"symbol","title":"keepScreenOn"},"doc://net.doo.ScanbotSDK/documentation/ScanbotSDK":{"url":"\/documentation\/scanbotsdk","kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"text":"Version: 8.0.4","type":"text"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/net.doo.ScanbotSDK\/documentation\/ScanbotSDK","type":"topic","role":"collection","title":"ScanbotSDK"}},"variantOverrides":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}],"patch":[{"op":"replace","path":"\/identifier\/interfaceLanguage","value":"occ"},{"op":"replace","value":"Instance Property","path":"\/metadata\/roleHeading"},{"op":"replace","value":"keepScreenOn","path":"\/metadata\/title"},{"op":"replace","value":"property","path":"\/metadata\/symbolKind"},{"op":"replace","value":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"keepScreenOn"}],"path":"\/metadata\/fragments"},{"op":"add","value":null,"path":"\/topicSections"},{"op":"add","value":null,"path":"\/relationshipsSections"},{"op":"add","value":null,"path":"\/seeAlsoSections"},{"op":"replace","value":{"declarations":[{"platforms":["iOS"